canning mirror during the integration time of 300 s per detector. The total\nintegration time of 1500 seconds is split among the three NIR wavelengths\nbands. DUNE has been proposed to ESA's Cosmic Vision program and has been\njointly selected with SPACE for an ESA Assessment Phase which has led to the\njoint Euclid mission concept.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jul 2008 09:39:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
