evolving into an OB\nassociation. Bochum 1 can be a missing link connecting early star cluster\ndissolution with the formation of low-mass OB associations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jul 2008 11:51:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
